hymns.title: No Title
verses: Na kuhinga mulandu wa baka- wubi

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Ngwendi, na tuzila vali na mashwa.
Na vimbangje lalo vali na mena

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Na citele ca mu mbunge cinahu

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Mwaka ni mwao muyilu na Yesu

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Na bantu ni mwabo baka mwitabila
Na myaka yayingi bantu ba litunga
Wuluno mu mwana wa lizu lya yesu

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Mwaka ni mwao uli na name

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Ngwe mwene wa mwilu ya vimyene

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Bali mu wuwahe wa mwene yetu;
Ngoboni ha kumona niye mwine ngovu,

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Nga tukenda vwino na mezi a Njambi
Na cimo cihasa kwiza ku li yetu

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Ku litala lya bantu ba nyambi bayo
Kowa kulila na kukola na kufwa,
Ku litala lyaliwahe lya nyambi liyo.
Tushiyenu kuhaka kwa byuma bya wuluno,
Tilamina kuli Yesu, niko kuli byabiwahe,

hymns.title: No Title
verses: E, tulemesa lizina lya Mwene Yesu

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Ove mukwetu ove mukwetu tata lelo
Mu lizina , mu lizina lya mwene yesu
Mwene ye yesu kutukenga mema mema
Mwene Yesu Mwene Yesu omwo eja

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Muje mwilu, muje mwilu, muje mwilu
Na Njambi, na Njambi, na Njambi

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Na wumi wa Nyambi wa muyilu

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Mwene Yesu aswana myaka na myaka

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Nambe ku vyeseko na ku vushonde,

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Njili na nzili yak u kwovola

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Njitokese too mu mbunge yangngeci njijelevene

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Ku mukulo wan donga ya mwonyo

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Veya ovo kun donga ya kutsa

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Mu litala lya tate matala amengi

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Zazi la ku luka li se li pazuzi.
Mu nyakalale! Lu se lu hupuzwi,
Ka lilato, mulimu u lu potezi.
A lu amuhele jesu ka tumelo.
Mu nyakalale! Ka baka la luna
Jesu kreste u tile ka bubotana

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Ki man` ya swana ni wena?
Ha yo ya swana ni wena.
Ha yo ya swana ni wena
Ha yo ya swana ni wena.
Cwale ni ka ku sa fela,
H`a yo ya swana ni wena.

hymns.title: No Title
verses: Ku njuvo ya tate kwili milili;
Atuwane cili ngu mu ngila yendi
